ygData.subject: Re: Freeport Sewers
ygData.msgSnippet: EQVault only has surface maps, like you find in the manual.  I am looking for a map of underneath Freeport, ie the Necro, Rogue, Shadow Knight guidl
ygData.messageBody:
EQVault only has surface maps, like you find in the
manual. I am looking for a map of underneath Freeport,
ie the Necro, Rogue, Shadow Knight guidl placements, and
an overall map of where everything is and how to get
from West Gate to East Gate through the sewer system.
I do not wish to be KOS by a random NPC when I go
through Freeport and have to try to get back through.
I do not know my way well enough to do it without a map.

--
Templarus
4th level Dark Elf Enchanter
Bertoxulous
